prehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is just the spacer used to separate lines in the log. If you don\u0027t see any specific textures listed in between, you need to hover over your mouse on the element you want to grab (if using the hotkey D.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lenaic","CreatedById":233548,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-08T16:48:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni don\u0027t know why but the mod juste dose not work, my game is stock no other mod exept HUD, Harmony, ZTheme and module manager everything is in the gamedata folder. i just don\u0027t know what to do ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-05-09T11:18:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224387878\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216056\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221715186918\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022233548\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lenaic\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, lenaic said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni don\u0027t know why but the mod juste dose not work, my game is stock no other mod exept HUD, Harmony, ZTheme and module manager everything is in the gamedata folder. i just don\u0027t know what to do ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo help us find out where the problem is, could you please tell us which version of KSP you are using (HR doesn\u0027t work below 1.8), and give us a few screenshots? Thanks. (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/83212-how-to-get